A real-world scenario when the site fails

BUG REPORT 1

Title:        Login Portal fails to load during occasional service outage

Description:   Clicking “Login” leads to timeout or error, login portal doesn’t appear

Steps:    1.  Navigate to https://www.fnb.co.za    2.  Click “Login”   3. Observe no page load or timeout

Expected Result:   Login portal loads successfully.

Actual Result:  Page fails or times out

Status:   Fail

Priority:   High

